by being stupid.

106
00:14:40.229 --> 00:14:42.324
- No, sir.
- "No, sir."

107
00:14:47.111 --> 00:14:50.549
It says here that
you've been decorated.

108
00:14:50.573 --> 00:14:51.900
Yes, sir.

109
00:14:54.410 --> 00:14:56.588
And they sent you here
to be posted?

110
00:14:56.671 --> 00:14:59.174
Actually, sir,
I'm here at my own request.

111
00:14:59.524 --> 00:15:01.927
Really? Why?

112
00:15:02.376 --> 00:15:04.721
I've always wanted
to see the frontier.

113
00:15:05.421 --> 00:15:07.641
You want to see the frontier?

114
00:15:08.007 --> 00:15:11.144
Yes, sir.
Before it's gone.

115
00:15:17.667 --> 00:15:20.278
Such a smart lad,
coming straight to me.

116
00:15:26.859 --> 00:15:30.397
Sir... knight,

117
00:15:31.447 --> 00:15:34.063
I am sending you
on a knight's errand.

118
00:15:35.576 --> 00:15:37.738
You will report to captain cargill

119
00:15:38.120 --> 00:15:41.132
at the furthermost
outpost of the realm,

120
00:15:41.249 --> 00:15:42.717
Fort Sedgewick.

121
00:15:44.919 --> 00:15:48.431
My personal seal
will assure your safety

122
00:15:48.464 --> 00:15:51.685
