they took all our horses.

204
00:28:10.080 --> 00:28:12.460
You stayed after
all the others deserted.

205
00:28:14.418 --> 00:28:18.049
You stayed after
the army failed to resupply us.

206
00:28:21.425 --> 00:28:24.347
I have looked for that wagon
from Fort Hayes,

207
00:28:24.594 --> 00:28:26.266
just as you have,

208
00:28:26.555 --> 00:28:28.601
day after miserable day.

209
00:28:31.643 --> 00:28:34.315
