Let's unload the wagon.

234
00:33:10.755 --> 00:33:13.175
What?
What, and leave it all here?

235
00:33:14.676 --> 00:33:16.303
I'm staying, too.

236
00:33:16.761 --> 00:33:19.056
There ain't nothing here, lieutenant.

237
00:33:19.531 --> 00:33:22.142
No, not at the moment.

238
00:33:22.492 --> 00:33:24.186
We don't know what's happened.

239
00:33:24.477 --> 00:33:26.505
So, so, l--
Things--

240
00:33:26.688 --> 00:33:29.149
Things being as they are,

241
00:33:29.341 --> 00:33:32.027
we might as well just turn around
and get headed back.

242
00:33:32.527 --> 00:33:35.264
- This is my post.
- "This is my post"?

243
00:33:35.530 --> 00:33:37.074
This is my post.

244
00:33:38.717 --> 00:33:40.452
"This is my post"?

245
00:33:40.535 --> 00:33:43.739
Jesus H. Christ.
What, are you crazy, boy?

246
00:33:43.839 --> 00:33:45.165
Lieutenant.

247
00:33:47.575 --> 00:33:49.094
Fast son of a bitch.

248
00:33:50.078 --> 00:33:51.834
- Jesus H. Christ!
- This is my post.

249
00:33:51.921 --> 00:33:53.457
All right, put it down.
Put it down.

250
00:33:53.548 --> 00:33:55.308
And these are the
post provisions, all right?

251
00:33:55.383 --> 00:33:57.590
Now, get your ass off the wagon...

252
00:33:57.677 --> 00:33:59.508
- Put it down!
- and help me unload.

253
00:33:59.596 --> 00:34:01.723
We're just having a conversation.
Now put it down.

254
00:34:53.400 --> 00:34:55.151
I'll let them know where you are.

255
00:34:56.461 --> 00:34:57.654
Good.

256
00:35:00.281 --> 00:35:01.866
Good luck, lieutenant.

257
00:35:03.785 --> 00:35:04.936
